Sky blue and white.

251
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:40,540
Sky blue and white.

252
00:21:40,540 --> 00:21:42,050
What's your favorite drink?

253
00:21:42,050 --> 00:21:43,570
Strawberry yogurt smoothie.

254
00:21:43,570 --> 00:21:45,460
Strawberry yogurt smoothie.

255
00:21:45,460 --> 00:21:47,680
By the way, how many questions do you have left?

256
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:50,800
♫ Blooms and the season ♫

257
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:54,590
♫ Keeps repeating itself ♫

258
00:21:54,590 --> 00:21:56,190
Are you really going to ask all of these?

259
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:59,300
Of course!

260
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:02,400
- Just one moment.
- Okay.

261
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:06,710
[101) Could you...]

262
00:22:07,910 --> 00:22:12,290
Next question.

263
00:22:12,290 --> 00:22:17,550
[Could you love me for eternity?]

264
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:20,950
♫ Even if I'm born again ♫

265
00:22:20,950 --> 00:22:23,410
[Next Story]
It didn't feel realistic.

266
00:22:23,410 --> 00:22:27,220
What was real? What was fiction?

267
00:22:27,220 --> 00:22:29,370
Or was it all just a dream?

268
00:22:29,370 --> 00:22:32,250
Why didn't you tell me from the start?

269
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:36,970
Why were you so mean to me? Why did you change your mind?

270
00:22:36,970 --> 00:22:41,680
I thought we felt the same, but now I don't know anymore.

271
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:46,370
Do you want to go with me? You originally wanted to attend graduate school there.

272
00:22:46,370 --> 00:22:48,610
Let's go back together.

273
00:22:48,610 --> 00:22:54,000
How long are you going to be around Ha Yeon using the excuse you're his friend? Don't you think that's cowardly?

274
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:56,060
That's why I'm not going to be his friend anymore.

275
00:22:56,060 --> 00:23:00,180
Ha Yeon and I are going back to America together.

276
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:02,350
I used to think like this.

277
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:05,480
To simply put it, "I'll go see you because I miss you."

278
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:12,290
But now, I think I may have been selfish.

279
00:23:12,290 --> 00:23:16,870
I learned that, although my feelings are important,

280
00:23:16,870 --> 00:23:19,820
the other person's feeling of wanting to see me or not is more important.

281
00:23:24,530 --> 00:23:31,430
♫ On an especially bright night ♫

282
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:40,910
♫ You said you'll stay by my side ♫

283
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:48,900
♫ Your eyes overfilling  ♫

284
00:23:48,900 --> 00:24:00,050
♫  With sincerity, I remember it ♫
